CODE.item: DATA: IT_TEXTO TYPE TABLE OF TLINE,
SELECT BUKRS BELNR GJAHR BLART BLDAT BUDAT TCODE XBLNR
AND ( TCODE = 'MIRO' OR TCODE = 'FB60' OR TCODE = 'FB65').
IF SY-SUBRC = 0 AND IT_BKPF IS NOT INITIAL.
SELECT BUKRS BELNR GJAHR BUZEI BUZID TXGRP KTOSL SGTXT LIFNR MATNR
WERKS MENGE MEINS EBELN EBELP BWKEY DMBE2 BUPLA FROM BSEG
IF SY-SUBRC = 0 AND IT_BSEG IS NOT INITIAL.
SELECT BELNR GJAHR BUKRS LFBNR LFGJA FROM RSEG
IF SY-SUBRC = 0 AND IT_RSEG IS NOT INITIAL.
SELECT GJAHR BELNR FRBNR LIFNR FROM EKBZ
IF SY-SUBRC = 0 AND IT_EKBZ IS NOT INITIAL.
SELECT LIFNR NAME1 ORT01 PSTLZ REGIO STRAS ADRNR KUNNR
SELECT EBELN BSART LIFNR FROM EKKO
IF SY-SUBRC = 0 AND IT_EKKO IS NOT INITIAL.
SELECT EBELN EBELP MATNR FROM EKPO
SELECT BUKRS BELNR GJAHR BUZEI TXGRP SHKZG HWBAS FWSTE
SELECT LIFNR NAME1 ORT01 PSTLZ REGIO STRAS ADRNR KUNNR
IF SY-SUBRC = 0 AND IT_LFA1 IS NOT INITIAL.
SELECT SPRAS LAND1 BLAND BEZEI FROM T005U
SELECT MATNR SPRAS MAKTX FROM MAKT
SELECT MATNR WERKS STEUC FROM MARC
SELECT WERKS NAME1 KUNNR LIFNR STRAS PSTLZ ORT01 REGIO
SELECT BUKRS BRANCH GSTIN FROM J_1BBRANCH
IF SY-SUBRC = 0 AND IT_LFA1 IS NOT INITIAL .
SELECT ADDRNUMBER NAME1 CITY2 STREET HOUSE_NUM1 REGION
APPEND LINES OF IT_BSEG TO IT_BSEG1.
DELETE IT_BSEG1 WHERE LIFNR IS INITIAL.
LOOP AT IT_BSEG INTO WA_BSEG WHERE MATNR <> '' .
READ TABLE IT_BSEG1 INTO WA_BSEG1 WITH KEY
LOOP AT IT_TEXTO INTO WA_TEXTO ." index 1 .
READ TABLE IT_T005U INTO WA_T005U WITH KEY SPRAS = 'EN'
READ TABLE IT_LFA12 INTO WA_LFA12 WITH KEY
READ TABLE IT_J_1BBRANCH INTO WA_J_1BBRANCH WITH KEY
READ TABLE IT_MAKT INTO WA_MAKT WITH KEY
READ TABLE IT_MARC INTO WA_MARC WITH KEY
LOOP AT IT_BSET INTO WA_BSET WHERE BUKRS = WA_BSEG-BUKRS
WA_FINAL-IGST_RATE = WA_BSET-KBETR / 10 . "#EC CI_FLDEXT_OK[2610650] added by SPLABAP during code remedation
WA_FINAL-CGST_RATE = WA_BSET-KBETR / 10 . "#EC CI_FLDEXT_OK[2610650] added by SPLABAP during code remedation
WA_FINAL-SGST_RATE = WA_BSET-KBETR / 10 ."#EC CI_FLDEXT_OK[2610650] added by SPLABAP during code remedation
AMT_IN_RND = ( TAX_TOT + STOTAL + CTOTAL + ITOTAL ). "#EC CI_FLDEXT_OK[2610650]
APPEND LINES OF IT_FINAL TO IT_FINAL2.
DELETE IT_FINAL2 WHERE SGTXT IS INITIAL.
DELETE IT_FINAL WHERE SGTXT IS INITIAL.
